5249:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c **** 
5250:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****     /* THIS FUNCTION MUST BE CALLED WITH THE
5251:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****      * SCHEDULER SUSPENDED AND THE QUEUE BEING ACCESSED LOCKED. */
5252:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c **** 
5253:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****     /* Place the event list item of the TCB in the appropriate event list.
