5258:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****      * Normally, the xItemValue of a TCB's ListItem_t members is:
5259:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****      *      xItemValue = ( configMAX_PRIORITIES - uxPriority )
